# x'' + 0.6x = 0*
using DifferentialEquations*
*
function lorenz!(du, u, p, t)*
a = p*
du[1] = u[2]*
du[2] = -a*u[1]*
end*
*
const x = 0.4*
const y = 2.1*
u0 = [x, y]*
*
p = (0.6)*
tspan = (0.0, 51.0)*
prob = ODEProblem(lorenz!, u0, tspan, p)*
sol = solve(prob, dtmax = 0.05)*
*
using Plots; gr()*
*
# *
plot(sol)*
savefig("lab4_julia_1.png")*
*
# *
plot(sol, vars=(2,1))*
savefig("lab4_julia_1_phase.png")*
****:*
# x'' + x' + 0.4x = 0*
using DifferentialEquations*
*
function lorenz!(du, u, p, t)*
a, b = p*
du[1] = u[2]*
du[2] = -a*du[1] - b*u[1] *
end*
*
const x = 0.4*
const y = 2.1*
u0 = [x, y]*
*
p = (sqrt(1), 0.4)*
tspan = (0.0, 51.0)*
prob = ODEProblem(lorenz!, u0, tspan, p)*
sol = solve(prob, dtmax = 0.05)*
*
using Plots; gr()*
*
# *
plot(sol)*
savefig("lab4_julia_2.png")*
*
# *
plot(sol, vars=(2,1))*
savefig("lab4_julia_2_ph.png")*
****:*
# x'' + 5x' + x = 0.5cos(2t)*
using DifferentialEquations*
*
function lorenz!(du, u, p, t)*
a, b = p*
du[1] = u[2]*
du[2] = -a*du[1] - b*u[1] + 0.7*sin(3*t)*
end*
*
const x = 0.4*
const y = 2.1*
u0 = [x, y]*
*
p = (sqrt(1), 10)*
tspan = (0.0, 51.0)*
prob = ODEProblem(lorenz!, u0, tspan, p)*
sol = solve(prob, dtmax = 0.05)*
*
using Plots; gr()*
*
# *
plot(sol)*
savefig("lab4_julia_3.png")*
*
# *
plot(sol, vars=(2,1))*
savefig("lab4_julia_3_phase.png")*

//case1: x''+ 4.3x = 0*
model lab4_1 *
//x'' + g* x' + w^2* x = f(t) *
//w - *
//g - *
parameter Real w = sqrt(4.30); *
parameter Real g =0; *
*
parameter Real x0 = -0.3; *
parameter Real y0 = 1.3; *
*
Real x(start=x0); *
Real y(start=y0); *
*
// f(t) *
function f *
input Real t ; *
output Real res; *
algorithm *
res := 0; *
end f; *
*
equation *
der(x) = y; *
der(y) = -w*w*x - g*y + f(time); *
end lab4_1;*
****:*
//case2: x'' + x' + 20x = 0*
model lab4_2*
*
parameter Real w = sqrt(20.00); *
parameter Real g = 1; *
*
parameter Real x0 = -0.3; *
parameter Real y0 = 1.3; *
*
Real x(start=x0); *
Real y(start=y0); *
*
// f(t) *
function f *
input Real t ; *
output Real res; *
algorithm *
res := 0; *
end f; *
*
equation *
der(x) = y; *
der(y) = -w*w*x - g*y + f(time); *
*
end lab4_2;*
****:*
//case3: x'' + x' + 8.8x = 0.7sin(3t)*
model lab4_3*
*
parameter Real w = sqrt(8.80); *
parameter Real g = 1; *
*
parameter Real x0 = -0.3; *
parameter Real y0 = 1.3; *
*
Real x(start=x0); *
Real y(start=y0); *
*
// f(t) *
function f *
input Real t ; *
output Real res; *
algorithm *
res := 0.7*sin(3*t); // 3 *
end f; *
*
equation *
der(x) = y; *
der(y) = -w*w*x - g*y - f(time); *
end lab4_3*
